"""Activity: SFML Anatomy

SFML is a graphics library, not a language feature -- it hands you a window, an event queue, and a canvas you draw shapes onto every frame. This activity builds the mental model you need before your course project: the game loop, the event queue, the coordinate system, and the handful of objects (Vector2f, shapes, textures, sprites, Color) that everything else is built from.
"""
